@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
[*] --> Created
Created --> Pending : approve
Created : entry / log inventory
Pending --> Delivered : cancel
Delivered --> Completed : process
Delivered : entry / log inventory
Completed --> Closed : approve
Completed : entry / log inventory
Closed --> Draft : reject
Closed : entry / log inventory
Draft --> [*]
@enduml